data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with loft/bonus room features 2 bedrooms downstairs and primary bedroom upstairs. There is a full bathroom downstairs with two sinks, and new shower/tub combo. The living areas, hallway and downstairs bedrooms have newer laminate wood looking plank flooring. The living room is spacious with ceiling fan, fireplace and access to the backyard and dining area. The dining area is conveniently located off the kitchen, with newer dishwasher, refrigerator and gas oven/stove combo. Upstairs the loft/bonus area can be used for a variety of things, there is even extra closet storage and additional, easy access into the attic complete with standing room that may provide the possibility of adding another room or more storage. The primary bedroom has a cedar lined, walk-in closet and attached bath with walk in shower. The backyard is a clean slate ready for you to build your dream space.
